tooltipText:
Conjures a massive flaming rock before sending it hurling toward target location. Upon impact, it deals $hit:Mage_Meteor_Landing_Hit_AOE$ and applies $effect:Status_Conflagrating$ to targets with $effect:Status_BurningStat.hide$

After landing, it continues to roll forward for its remaining distance, dealing damage to enemies along its path.
name: Mage_Meteor
